  "texts": [
    "4.2.5Effectiveness Comparison: GPT-3.5 vs.GPT-4.",
    "Figure 3: (9) illustrates a comparison of jailbreak prompts' success rates on GPT-3.5 and GPT-4 based on patterns.",
    "For GPT-3.5, the RE, TRANS, and PROG patterns yield high success rates of 82%, 76%, and 54%.",
    "Conversely, GPT-4 finds the TC, LOGIC, and RE patterns most effective, albeit at lower rates of 40%, 34%, and 32%.",
    "RE proves effective for both models, possibly using a pretending strategy to conceal the intent of accessing prohibited content."
